{"tid":673741,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個突飛猛進嘅經歷","createTime":"2018-05-22T06:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T13:20:33.000Z","uid":83933,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0e20b8ec9a70934c6fe7450a5d6ac18855d7d8","tid":673741,"uid":83933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:02:00.000Z","msg":"可以包含唔同方面，可能係讀書，事業，運動，係一段短時間內好集中做一件事令到自己係果方面突飛猛進，好似突然打通任督二脈咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先，中四上學期果時平均分唔合格，結果聖誕假去自修室溫返啲自己唔識嘅野，下學期平均分升咗十分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fffb42bb2c9402ce0f1f6d7e59a3f4a6891d11","tid":673741,"uid":11217,"like":8,"dislike":15,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5128f67c59c7cf38aff0b0e743287e8b987061c","tid":673741,"uid":36296,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"我既磅數"},{"pid":"31c048a15c0ef78f1645f40321edaecbd198bcda","tid":673741,"uid":83933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以包含唔同方面，可能係讀書，事業，運動，係一段短時間內好集中做一件事令到自己係果方面突飛猛進，好似突然打通任督二脈咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先，中四上學期果時平均分唔合格，結果聖誕假去自修室溫返啲自己唔識嘅野，下學期平均分升咗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十分</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n【名稱】：突飛猛進<br />\n<br />\n【拼音】：tū fēi měng j&igrave;n<br />\n<br />\n【注音】：ㄊㄨ　ㄈㄟ　ㄇㄥˇ　ㄐ｜ㄣˋ<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">【釋義】：突、猛：形容急速。形容進步和發展特別迅速</span>。<br />\n<br />\n【出處】：<br />\n<br />\n【例子】：社會主義制度促進了我國生產力的～的發展。（毛澤東《關於正確處理人民內部矛盾的問題》）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 受教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/